  <brief_title>Weight-reduction Intervention in Asthmatic Children With Overweight/Obesity</brief_title>
  <official_title>Secondary Prevention of Asthma in Overweight/Obese Children by a Combined Dietary-behavioural-physical Activity Intervention</official_title>
