  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the efficacy of a multifactorial intervention with
      weight reduction, behavioural therapy, and physical exercise on the severity and control of
      asthma in obese children.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
